These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-6-1::.
House: wooden, gothic-revival, futuristic
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, light-blue, pink
1. the wooden house is somewhere to the left of the person who likes pink##5
2. the futuristic house is somewhere to the left of the person who likes azure##5
3. the person who likes light-blue is not the futuristic house##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage    | wooden | futuristic | gothic-revival   |
| Transport   | light-blue         | pink   | azure |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-6-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, sudoku, collecting
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, water
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is not the person drinking water##6
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |    3     |
| Food          | traveling    | collecting  | sudoku     |
| Movie-Genre   | fanta | coffee | water |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-6-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, coffee, lemonade
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, grey, white
1. the person drinking coffee is not the person who likes fuchsia##6
2. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking coffee and the person who likes white##2
3. the person who likes white is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
4. the person who likes white is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | coffee    | lemonade | juice |
| Music-Genre   | grey | fuchsia   | white     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-6-4::.
3 different games are played: snooker, backgammon, billiard
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, action, epic
1. the person playing backgammon is not the person watching epic movies##6
2. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the right of the person playing backgammon##5
3. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the person playing snooker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | backgammon  | snooker | billiard      |
| Nationality   | action | epic  | crime |

