.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-6-5::.
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, whist, billiard
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, august, march
1. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person playing billiard##5
2. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person playing billiard and the person who's birthday is in january##2
3. the person playing mah-jongg is not the person who's birthday is in august##6
4. the person playing whist is not the person who's birthday is in march##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage   | whist | mah-jongg       | billiard |
| Food       | january   | march | august   |

