.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-6-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, french, argentine
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, 7up, lemonade
1. the french is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the french is not the person drinking mirinda##6
4. the argentine is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking mirinda##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |
| Hobby         | french | argentine | italian |
| Music-Genre   | 7up     | lemonade        | mirinda       |

