3. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
4. the person driving the car is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |
| Beverage      | jet-ski | car  | train |
| Movie-Genre   | goat  | rabbit | pony   |

