.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-6-20::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, crime, scientific
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, golf, badminton
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person watching family movies is the person watching family movies##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is not the person watching family movies##6
4. the person watching scientific movies is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is cricket##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food    | family   | scientific | crime |
| Hobby   | badminton | golf | cricket |

 